==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|encourag|ing}}

# To mentally [[support]]; to [[motivate]].
#:''I '''encouraged''' him during his race.''
# To recommend.
#:''We '''encourage''' the use of bicycles in town centre.''

====Antonyms====
*[[discourage]]

